# Frontend Boundaries

- Frontend work may include React, TypeScript, hooks, pages, components, and client services.
- Keep `VITE_*` variables stable unless explicitly asked to change them.
- Do not invent deployment or infrastructure edits from frontend work alone.
- If frontend work needs backend, DB, or env changes, state that clearly.
- Prefer maintainable structure over one-off generated code.
